    "template": "{{#if activeSlide '===' '0'}} {{assignVar 'slide1' 'active'}} {{/if}} {{#if activeSlide '===' '1'}} {{assignVar 'slide2' 'active'}} {{/if}} {{#if activeSlide '===' '2'}} {{assignVar 'slide3' 'active'}} {{/if}} {{#if activeSlide '===' '3'}} {{assignVar 'slide4' 'active'}} {{/if}} <ul> <li>{{getVar 'slide1'}}</li> <li>{{getVar 'slide2'}}</li> <li>{{getVar 'slide3'}}</li> <li>{{getVar 'slide4'}}</li> </ul> <div class='homepage-hero-banner' data-activeSlide='{{activeSlide}}'> <div class='single-hero-banner {{getVar 'slide1'}}'> <div class='banner-image'> <img src='{{image1.src}}' alt='{{alt_text1}}'/> </div> <div class='banner-details'> <h4 class='hero-title'>{{title1}}</h4> <div class='hero-description'>{{{description1}}}</div>{{#if cta_text1}}<a class='hero-link' href='{{cta_link1}}'>{{cta_text1}}</a>{{/if}} </div> </div> <div class='single-hero-banner {{getVar 'slide2'}}'> <div class='banner-image'> <img src='{{image2.src}}' alt='{{alt_text2}}'/> </div> <div class='banner-details'> <h4 class='hero-title'>{{title2}}</h4> <div class='hero-description'>{{{description2}}}</div>{{#if cta_text2}}<a class='hero-link' href='{{cta_link2}}'>{{cta_text2}}</a>{{/if}} </div> </div> <div class='single-hero-banner {{getVar 'slide3'}}'> <div class='banner-image'> <img src='{{image3.src}}' alt='{{alt_text3}}'/> </div> <div class='banner-details'> <h4 class='hero-title'>{{title3}}</h4> <div class='hero-description'>{{{description3}}}</div>{{#if cta_text3}}<a class='hero-link' href='{{cta_link3}}'>{{cta_text3}}</a>{{/if}} </div> </div> <div class='single-hero-banner {{getVar 'slide4'}}'> <div class='banner-image'> <img src='{{image4.src}}' alt='{{alt_text4}}'/> </div> <div class='banner-details'> <h4 class='hero-title'>{{title4}}</h4> <div class='hero-description'>{{{description4}}}</div>{{#if cta_text4}}<a class='hero-link' href='{{cta_link4}}'>{{cta_text4}}</a>{{/if}} </div> </div> </div>"
